---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Experiences — Made the Weekend"
  description="The bookable experiences worth planning a UK weekend around. Tried first; the ones that don't live up to it never make the page."
>
<section class="page-head">
  <div class="inner">
    <svg class="page-motif" width="120" height="44" viewBox="0 0 120 44" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
  <path d="M4 40 C 30 34, 40 22, 60 20 C 74 18.5, 82 17, 89 14" stroke="#E0A45C" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-dasharray="0.5 7" opacity="0.8"></path>
  <path d="M98 2 C 101.3 2, 104 4.7, 104 8 C 104 12.5, 98 17.5, 98 17.5 C 98 17.5, 92 12.5, 92 8 C 92 4.7, 94.7 2, 98 2 Z" stroke="#E0A45C" stroke-width="1.4" fill="none"></path>
  <circle cx="98" cy="7.8" r="1.8" fill="#E0A45C"></circle>
</svg>
    <p class="eyebrow">Experiences</p>
    <h1>The one thing to book before you go</h1>
    <p class="lede">The bookable thing that makes a weekend. We add one only after it's earned its place; if it didn't live up to it, it isn't here.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="dark" style="padding-top:clamp(48px,7vw,72px);padding-bottom:clamp(64px,9vw,100px);">
  <div class="wrap">
    <a class="feat" href="/coming-soon">
      <div class="img" data-ph="Seals at Blakeney Point"></div>
      <div class="shade"></div>
      <div class="cap">
        <p class="eyebrow">Featured · North Norfolk</p>
        <h2>The seal boats from Morston Quay</h2>
        <p>Grey seals hauled out on the point, a flat-bottomed boat and a skipper who's done it for thirty years. Book the first sailing; the light is better and the crowds aren't up.</p>
        <p class="meta">Half a morning · pairs with the Holkham guide</p>
      </div>
    </a>
    <div class="grid3"><a class="g-card" href="/coming-soon">
  <div class="thumb"><div class="img" data-ph="Canoe on the Wye, early light"></div></div>
  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
    <p class="eyebrow">Monmouthshire</p>
    <h3>Canoeing the Wye at dawn</h3>
    <p class="meta">Full day · Symonds Yat to Monmouth</p>
  </div>
</a><a class="g-card" href="/coming-soon">
  <div class="thumb"><div class="img" data-ph="Dartmoor night sky"></div></div>
  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
    <p class="eyebrow">Devon</p>
    <h3>A guided dark-sky night on Dartmoor</h3>
    <p class="meta">One evening · new moon weekends</p>
  </div>
</a><a class="g-card" href="/coming-soon">
  <div class="thumb"><div class="img" data-ph="Sea kayaks below St Davids cliffs"></div></div>
  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
    <p class="eyebrow">Pembrokeshire</p>
    <h3>Sea kayaking from St Davids</h3>
    <p class="meta">Half day · caves, seals, no experience needed</p>
  </div>
</a><a class="g-card" href="/coming-soon">
  <div class="thumb"><div class="img" data-ph="Rooftop pool, Bath at dusk"></div></div>
  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
    <p class="eyebrow">Somerset</p>
    <h3>The rooftop baths after dark</h3>
    <p class="meta">Two hours · book the last session</p>
  </div>
</a><a class="g-card" href="/coming-soon">
  <div class="thumb"><div class="img" data-ph="Shoreline foraging, Suffolk"></div></div>
  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
    <p class="eyebrow">Suffolk</p>
    <h3>Foraging the Suffolk shoreline</h3>
    <p class="meta">Half day · ends with lunch you found</p>
  </div>
</a><a class="g-card" href="/coming-soon">
  <div class="thumb"><div class="img" data-ph="Ghyll scrambling, Langdale"></div></div>
  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
    <p class="eyebrow">Cumbria</p>
    <h3>Ghyll scrambling in Langdale</h3>
    <p class="meta">Half day · wetsuit provided, nerve not</p>
  </div>
</a></div>
    <p class="disc-line">Booking through links on this page earns us a small commission at no cost to you. It never changes what we recommend.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
</Base>
